1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,600
Before the Three Kingdoms,
three unknown men made one oath.

2
00:00:02,600 --> 00:00:05,800
Guan Yu came to enlist.
Liu Bei and Zhang Fei saw the same road ahead.

3
00:00:05,800 --> 00:00:07,200
In a peach garden,

4
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,200
they swore brotherhood
before heaven and earth.

5
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:10,800
"We swear to die together."

6
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:13,400
With horses, iron, and five hundred volunteers,
the oath became an army.

7
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,000
And the three men walked into history.
